FBIS3-15365 "drsov043_r_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-043 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 Azerbaijan Trial on Aliyev Assassination Attempt Begins NC0303210694 Baku TURAN in English 1659 GMT 3 Mar 94 NC0303210694 Baku TURAN Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Baku (March 3) TURAN -- Recent arrests of the leaders of the PFA, Musavat and other opposition organizations testify to violation of democratic principles and freedom of speech in Azerbaijan, says the statement of Independent Democratic Party of Azerbaijan. The statement mentions that the authorities try to conceal military defeats and economic crisis and shift the blame onto a new enemy, opposition.
